&lt;li&gt;Solid, senior+ technical capability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good understanding of overall system architecture including backend systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross functional collaboration capability; ability to work across team / org / system boundaries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dynamic infrastructure and has been focused on building front-end design systems&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good to have experience on any frontend framework but Angular, NGRX and RXJS solid experience is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience on building UI components library&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
