we need engineers who can invent answers no one has thought of yet and find answers to the questions yet to be asked.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;normaltextrun&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;eop&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:200,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
