&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is someone who can be self-sufficient and product-minded. You will be working on cross-cutting problems that will require strong cross-team collaboration, both technically (security, cloud backends, and the Waymo Driver) and functionally (operations, product, legal, partnerships, policy &amp;amp; privacy) to develop and deliver business critical infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;
