&lt;p&gt;Support development, testing and evolution of mapping data in the simulator&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Improve / monitor the performance, scalability and the reliability of the simulator&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Design the long term architecture to fit the product to an increasing number of internal customers&lt;/p&gt;
