&lt;li&gt;Integrate and deploy ML models on the fleet, conduct end-to-end validation and on-field monitoring.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay up-to-date with the latest advancements in autonomous driving and machine learning, and be able quickly prototype, experiment and deploy novel SOTA solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with partner teams such as perception, research, simulation, and evaluation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor engineers in leading adoption of ML-based approaches for solving reasoning problems.&lt;/li&gt;
