&lt;li&gt;Monitor and improve the performance, scalability, testing, and the reliability of the platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with other engineers to design the long-term architecture of the system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
