&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience with C++ (or a willingness to learn)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Passion for working in cross functional environments that include nontechnical stakeholders&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
