&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-local-id=&quot;eb24617e-10c5-411b-ae52-42d76ce6e33f&quot; data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;listItem&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-local-id=&quot;e0a091139c21&quot; data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Give candid, constructive feedback that helps people grow while maintaining trust and psychological safety.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-local-id=&quot;f9bc2944-f6ec-4f16-ba8a-c81cac8eba35&quot; data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;listItem&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-local-id=&quot;b63a30064bb2&quot; data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Invest in career development by helping engineers build and execute on clear growth plans.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-local-id=&quot;3ba2dd77-980e-4d89-a528-c5449100706a&quot; data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;listItem&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
