&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BS in Computer Science, Robotics, Statistics, Physics, Math or another quantitative area&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong self-motivation to navigate complex systems and pursue open-ended problems to completion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ years of industry experience with&lt;br&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigating and modifying a large code base containing a variety of languages, such as C++, Python and SQL&lt;/li&gt;
