&lt;p&gt;Trip platform team specifically focus on building Waymo&#39;s core trip platform to support multiple high-growth use cases, including ride-hailing and delivery, across both 1st party and 3rd party B2B partners’ needs, enabling broader access to Waymo technology for more people and markets.&lt;/p&gt;
