&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement and scale Waymo&#39;s core trip platform to support multiple high-growth use cases, including ride-hailing and delivery, across both 1st party and 3rd party B2B partners’ needs, enabling broader access to Waymo technology for more people and markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and implement partner facing API services for various customer-hailing scenarios, including managing trip requests and calculating pickup and ride times; calculates the price of rides.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with external partners to jointly build great Waymo experiences on 3rd party platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop expertise in and make use of various Google technologies, like OnePlatform API, Borg, Spanner, Flume, and custom-built systems for our specific problems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
